<?xml version="1.0" encoding="utf-8"?>
<package xmlns="http://schemas.microsoft.com/packaging/2011/08/nuspec.xsd">
  <metadata>
    <id>DataverseMigrationScaffolder</id>
    <version>1.2026.7.6</version>
    <title>Dataverse Migration Scaffolder</title>
    <authors>Ryu Ohkawa</authors>
    <owners>Ryu Ohkawa</owners>
    <projectUrl>https://github.com/ryuohk/DataverseMigrationScaffolder</projectUrl>
    <iconUrl>https://raw.githubusercontent.com/ryuohk/DataverseMigrationScaffolder/main/images/logo.png</iconUrl>
    <license type="expression">MIT</license>
    <requireLicenseAcceptance>false</requireLicenseAcceptance>
    <description>XrmToolBox tool that scaffolds a SQL data-migration harness from Dataverse metadata: staging table and GUID mapping table DDL scripts batched strictly by dependency tier, plus truncate/teardown scripts, match-key indexes, a styled Excel data dictionary, and a Mermaid dependency diagram. Filters tables and columns by solution, remembers selections per environment, and is fully configurable (prefixes, match-key suffixes, dependency-ranking exclusions).</description>
    <summary>Scaffold SQL staging and GUID mapping tables from Dataverse metadata, batched by dependency tier - plus data dictionary, dependency diagram, and harness reset/teardown scripts.</summary>
    <releaseNotes>
1.2026.7.6: Solution picker improvements.
- Lists managed AND unmanaged solutions, with managed ones labeled "(managed)" - replaces the 1.2026.7.5 toggle
- Dropdown widens to fit long solution names

1.2026.7.5: "Include managed" toggle next to the Solution picker (managed solutions labeled; patches always excluded).

1.2026.7.4: Fix update loop - 1.2026.7.3 was packaged with a mismatched assembly version. Do not install 1.2026.7.3.

1.2026.7.3: Feedback round.
- Solution picker now lists only unmanaged solutions and excludes patches
- Generated SQL no longer emits GO separators or ON [PRIMARY]
- Selected output folder is displayed in the toolbar (full path on hover)
- Genericized example text in the dependency exclusions dialog
- Tooltips on every control, quick-start guide in the preview pane, clearer warnings panel

1.2026.7.2: Fix tool list icons (re-encoded PNG metadata images).

1.2026.7.1: Initial release.
- Staging and GUID mapping table DDL from Dataverse metadata (drop-and-recreate or create-if-missing)
- Strict one-dependency-tier-per-file batching for SSIS package sequencing; cycles broken by edge-dropping with deferred-update warnings
- Solution-based table and column filtering; per-environment remembered selections
- Configurable table prefixes and match-key suffixes; dependency-ranking exclusions
- Extra outputs: truncate script, teardown script, styled Excel data dictionary, Mermaid dependency diagram
- Guarded match-key indexes; session metadata cache; cancelable generation
    </releaseNotes>
    <copyright>Copyright © Ryu Ohkawa 2026</copyright>
    <tags>XrmToolBox Plugins Dataverse Migration SQL Staging DDL Scaffolder DataDictionary</tags>
    <dependencies>
      <dependency id="XrmToolBox" version="1.2025.10.74" />
    </dependencies>
  </metadata>
  <files>
    <!-- Only this tool's assembly - no SDK or XrmToolBox assemblies (Tool Library rule) -->
    <file src="DataverseMigrationScaffolder\bin\Release\DataverseMigrationScaffolder.dll" target="lib\net48\Plugins" />
  </files>
</package>
